  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game price was changed from Free to $5,99. This means reviews that were placed for the free version do not count for the positivity score anymore, but you can still check those (Very Positive) reviews out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Join the Discord server and tell me about your experiences, so the game can be improved accordingly!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DESTROY THE HOUSE OF YOUR NEIGHBOR</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To accomplish this you need the perfect strategy and find balance between making money and destruction. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow Cannabis in your Shed. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\">Enslave</span> Hire Aliens to Work for You. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Process Weed into a Variety of Products. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sell Products to Customers to Make Money. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy Upgrades and Machines from your Phone. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throw Furniture and other Objects at your Neighbor's House. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft new Powerful Objects in the Furnicombinator. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brew Potions for Crafting or to Power Machines. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch Out for Thieves Stealing your Orders. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Call the Police on your Neighbor. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make sure your own House isn't Burning to the Ground while you're Busy. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And so much more!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Online</i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Casual 1v1         <strong>[AVAILABLE]</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Casual 2v2        <strong>[AVAILABLE]</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Casual 3v3       <strong>[AVAILABLE]</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Casual 4v4        <strong>[AVAILABLE]</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oonky Revolution <strong>[AVAILABLE]</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Practice</i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tutorial <strong>[AVAILABLE]</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play Against AI <strong>[AVAILABLE]</strong></p></li></ul>",
